latestIgtvVideos.title: L’Oréal “24” infallible foundation review 💕
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
So I have been hearing this foundation is a good dupe of Estee Lauders Double wear... it really does have great coverage and a nice silky but matt finish to it. After applying a full face after this video I can confirm my makeup looked flawless! It hasn’t sat heavy On my skin and it hasn’t made me oily like a lot of high street brands can. I would rate this a strong 8/10 VERY IMPRESSED 🙌🏽
